      "rationale": "Primary QoI is the relative hemolysis index (RHI), a direct surrogate for clinical hemolysis accepted by FDA guidance and ASTM F1841. Power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger model parameterized with bovine blood data consistent with predicate device submissions. QoI relevance exceeds MRL 2 requirement."
